{"tid":1071230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警犬頭伸進短裙妹雙腿間查緝　網友：有異味？","createTime":"2019-03-21T08:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T11:14:18.000Z","uid":121473,"like":182,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"0a14b8a15393072cc42a9e9d2799d7343393567c","tid":1071230,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"泰國《臉書》粉絲團「แก้เซ็ง」分享了一張疑似警犬出任務查緝毒品的照片，並稱警犬相當盡忠職守。而網友看到照片後紛紛留言「裡面有毒品異味?」、「我想知道這隻狗狗會不會被臭暈」、「可憐的狗」、「我猜這隻狗是公的」、「能理解這個任務很重要」、「一定是偷藏毒品要吸出來」。<br />\n<br />\n另外有野網友說，看到這短裙妹的手臂，感覺是男的「會不會狗狗聞香腸」、「聞到彈出來了」，但有人解釋，是因為泰國女性都辛勤工作，所以才會有這樣的肌肉。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K4L8mnQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4L8mnQ.jpg&h=120b89fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自แก้เซ็ง臉書<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190321/1537048/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190321%2F1537048%2F&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3AQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=4a568cde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190321%2F1537048%2F&h=9af75abc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190321/1537048/</a>"},{"pid":"5cc79abe99ac2f9c5608e188db289c0efe27b0e5","tid":1071230,"uid":40470,"like":289,"dislike":1,"score":288,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:01:04.000Z","msg":"有腸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1c43032ae5cae2c4133daf3e53813e8f853443","tid":1071230,"uid":45788,"like":163,"dislike":1,"score":162,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:01:23.000Z","msg":"可能男人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aeeb0d9f6507e33368aab793b14e7b587feb95a","tid":1071230,"uid":11067,"like":135,"dislike":1,"score":134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"相入面全部雄性"},{"pid"